e\nperiod or phase modulation during the survey. On the other hand, surveys with a\ncadence to detect slightly changing light curves usually have a relatively\nsmall footprint. LSST's survey strategy, however, will allow for studying\nvariable stars in a way that makes population studies possible.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 27 Sep 2021 17:33:20 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 7 Oct 2021 21:25:42 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-01-05"}
