 Ne where the ratios are less than 0.1. The energy spectra are\ncalculated for both a Coulombic final electron state and a free final electron\nstate. The results indicate that the binding effects from the continuum state\nof the final electron are significant and can be comparable to those arising\nfrom the bound initial electron state.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 28 Sep 2021 03:07:45 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 7 Dec 2021 23:48:14 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-01-26"}
