ive areas of directly coupled SQUID magnetometers\nwith large washer-style pick-up loops. The latter agree to better than 7% with\nexperimentally-measured values, validating our measured value of $\\lambda(77)$\nand our inductance extraction methods.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 28 Sep 2021 10:16:06 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-09-29"}
