 that\nthe star-formation rate in the ISM varies in a complicated manner that depends\non the strength of the jet-ISM coupling and the jet break-out time-scale.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 28 Sep 2021 12:16:07 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 27 Oct 2021 02:15:33 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-10-28"}
